Detailed Description

Structure holding the configuration parameters of high resolution pwm pulse generation sub module.

Field Documentation

uint32_t CSL_EpwmHighResolutionCfg::cmpAHighResVal

Counter comparator A high-resolution bits for MEP step control. A min value of 1h is needed to enable HRPWM capabilities. Valid MEP range of operation 1-255h.

uint32_t CSL_EpwmHighResolutionCfg::delayBusSelect

Delay Bus Selection that selects which bus is used to select the delay for the PWM pulse. This can take values from the following enum CSL_EpwmHrDelayBusSelMode_t.

uint32_t CSL_EpwmHighResolutionCfg::delayMode

Delay Mode that selects which edge of the PWM pulse the delay is inserted. This can take values from the following enum CSL_EpwmHrDelayEdgeCtrl_t.

uint32_t CSL_EpwmHighResolutionCfg::pulseSelect

Pulse selection bits that selects which pulse to use for timing events in the HRPWM module.

uint32_t CSL_EpwmHighResolutionCfg::tbPhaseHighResVal

Time base phase high resolution value.
